    "description": "Skirmish Mayhem 是一款动作策略游戏，您可以在其中升级您的军械库，建造基地并建立一支军队来防御敌人的波浪。在征服银河系时，解锁更多地图、指挥官、武器、单位和建筑物。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >三个多元派系</h2>以沉迷于生物科学的 <strong>Virid</strong> 身份战斗，以神圣秩序 <strong>Sanctul</strong> 的身份征服，或以恶魔军团 <strong>Matulis</strong> 的身份播撒混乱。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124150/extras/90d2bb149204cbbfcd4a8598f6a76f80.poster.avif?t=1769271166\" width=800 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124150/extras/90d2bb149204cbbfcd4a8598f6a76f80.webm?t=1769271166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124150/extras/90d2bb149204cbbfcd4a8598f6a76f80.mp4?t=1769271166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗内外升级</h2>为您的指挥官配备大量武器，例如狙击枪、霰弹枪、激光、护盾，并在战斗过程中变得更强大。然后在战场之外升级派系的科技树，增加该派系的统计数据并解锁更强大的武器、建筑物和单位。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124150/extras/8bcc067d7e92ad075bb0808c629848cb.poster.avif?t=1769271166\" width=800 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124150/extras/8bcc067d7e92ad075bb0808c629848cb.webm?t=1769271166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124150/extras/8bcc067d7e92ad075bb0808c629848cb.mp4?t=1769271166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >击败独特的首领</h2>每个世界都有多个首领供您击败，从巨大的外星变种人到巨大的机器。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解锁更多内容！</h2>随着您的游玩，您将解锁新的战斗地图、新的机制和新的难度。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124150/extras/9474b720a89108500a9689ec5131d9c1.poster.avif?t=1769271166\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124150/extras/9474b720a89108500a9689ec5131d9c1.webm?t=1769271166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124150/extras/9474b720a89108500a9689ec5131d9c1.mp4?t=1769271166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
